{"tid":2497633,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"慘遭黑箱錯過IZ*ONE！　《PD48》韓初媛等3年成功以Cube新團出道","createTime":"2021-04-20T15:50:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-20T16:36:50.000Z","uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"397d19ba3a648043fbf411bfc7f6232a833a5c99","tid":2497633,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T15:50:46.000Z","msg":"南韓知名經紀公司CUBE娛樂旗下擁有BTOB、CLC、PENTAGON等團體，繼2018年推出(G)I-DLE後，睽違3年確定要再推出新女團「LIGHTSUM」，目前為止公開了6名成員，其中包含了2017年參加《THE UNIT》的珠賢以及在《PRODUCE 48》中慘成黑箱作業受害者，錯失以IZ*ONE一員出道機會的韓初媛（正名：韓霄瑗）。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5578/d5578080.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5578%2Fd5578080.jpg&h=a671e5e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲CUBE娛樂睽違三年推出新女團LIGHTSUM。（圖／翻攝LIGHTSUM官方IG）<br />\n<br />\n據悉，截至20日為止，CUBE娛樂一共公開了6名成員相雅、霄瑗、珠賢、池按、娜英、徽姸。其中珠賢在13歲時就曾以練習生身分參加選秀節目《THE UNIT》，以超齡的舞蹈實力在觀眾心目中留下強烈印象，隔年也參加了《Dancing High》。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5578/d5578081.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5578%2Fd5578081.jpg&h=6adbe579&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲珠賢曾參加選秀節目《THE UNIT》。（圖／翻攝LIGHTSUM官方IG）<br />\n<br />\n令一方面，霄瑗則是在《PRODUCE 48》展現了不俗的歌唱、RAP、舞蹈實力，具有反轉魅力，並成功闖進了總決賽，最終排名14名，直到先前《PRODUCE》系列證實作假，公開她真實最終排名為第6名，與前After School成員李佳恩成為該季的受害者，時隔3年終於成功出道，引發了韓網一片熱議。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5578/d5578079.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5578%2Fd5578079.jpg&h=6687311d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5578/d5578082.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5578%2Fd5578082.jpg&h=e454e29a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲霄瑗（韓初媛）成功出道。（圖／翻攝LIGHTSUM官方IG）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5578/d5578084.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5578%2Fd5578084.jpg&h=223beb1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲霄瑗在《PRODUCE 48》表現亮眼。（圖／翻攝《PD48》臉書）"},{"pid":"4dd12762d14eedc87c4740481e9a339314cbd422","tid":2497633,"uid":219225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T15:51:26.000Z","msg":"珠賢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2aba5dbb228d56b20422955c9ec4777442898833","tid":2497633,"uid":46435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T15:52:00.000Z","msg":"搞咩舒漫白左咁能多.."},{"pid":"660f6319c2ca755c5376119cc8cf11c7dfdaff37","tid":2497633,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2aba5dbb228d56b20422955c9ec4777442898833","tid":2497633,"uid":46435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T15:52:00.000Z","msg":"搞咩舒漫白左咁能多.."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T15:52:24.000Z","msg":"FILTER姐"},{"pid":"8fd841e56ddc759545a4f466eebf1218847f79a6","tid":2497633,"uid":34071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T16:24:23.000Z","msg":"得罪講句有少少似牙閪...<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8d052b33e0c0e5a20d50e993ac08b1868335ca9","tid":2497633,"uid":218941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T16:31:50.000Z","msg":"第一眼真係認唔出 白左咁多嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fbb6d888d983fa69afcb3a1bc1ce383b368df56","tid":2497633,"uid":3501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T16:36:50.000Z","msg":"點解個正名咁複雜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}